</figure>
<figure id="OSC_Astro_09_05_Basin">
<title>Caloris Basin.</title>
<media id="fs-id1170326170347" alt="Photograph of the Caloris Basin on Mercury. The circular, flat plain of Caloris Basin is surrounded by cratered highlands and rough terrain. A few impact craters are scattered over the smooth surface of the basin.">
