<exercise id="fs-id1170326097804">
<problem id="fs-id1170323856861">
<para id="fs-id1170326176302">In the future, astronomers discover a solid moon around a planet orbiting one of the nearest stars. This moon has a diameter of 1948 km and a mass of 1.6 × 10<sup>22</sup> kg. What is its density?</para>
